Package user.organizer

Class OrganizerPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • user.UserPresenter
      • user.attendee.AttendeePresenter
        • user.organizer.OrganizerPresenter
  • public class OrganizerPresenter
extends AttendeePresenter
    This class is a Presenter Class with specific functionality for Organizer Controllers. It handles asking for user input and printing any error messages.
